Class ParameterOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.storytron.uber.operator.Operator
      • com.storytron.uber.operator.ParameterOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Operator>

    public class ParameterOperator
extends Operator
    A ParamenterOperator is a reference to a parameter in a custom operator body. Therefore, it can appear only inside an operator body script.
